# Import Schema Conventions

- Disease object fields:
  - `disease_id`, `disease_name`, `key_symptoms`, `key_pulse`, `category`, `related_diseases`, `syndromes`
- Syndrome object fields:
  - `syndrome_id`, `disease_id`, `syndrome_name`, `symptoms`, `pathogenesis`, `treatment_method`, `prescription`, `key_symptom_analysis`
- `symptoms` shape:
  - `full_text`: string
  - `items`: array of `{ text: string, is_key: boolean }`
- `prescription` shape:
  - `primary`: string (required)
  - `alternative`: string or `null`
- Keep wording concise and clinical; do not drop key signs, pulse/tongue clues, or stage labels.
